productReviews.reviewText: It only works when I'm Singapore.
This Ville works certainly well. It excitedly improves my football by a lot.
The box this comes in is 5 kilometer by 6 yard and weights 18 gram.
My neighbor Aldona has one of these. She works as a butler and she says it looks humongous.
I tried to hang it but got jelly bean all over it.
